Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 在偷拍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太安靜了 反而睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用你的攝魂機…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個時間留住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪陪我?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我把杯子都帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光注意些蘩文縟節
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想輕鬆征戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個過分的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我惡作劇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管外面是下雨或下雪都把我關在家門外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連吃晚飯的時候都不開門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也算是替一直忙於工作的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格管教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 其實我知道一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在不被人發現的狀態下 從後面的窗戶進去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在還守著這個秘密 這話只跟你說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10加普就靠岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是把羅巴帶來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.55,0:04:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在贊巴尼號上是它自己做出的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎幺說呢 我在想見到他們時該用什麼表情才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經很出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…剛才是在誇我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你離別半年的故鄉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是尖端島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪裡打的電話?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…尖端島
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在姐姐在軍隊的宿舍裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我估計春也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我可以跟她聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打個電話之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 姐姐肯定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們打算在這裡停泊三天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用擔心你的划艇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去惹憲兵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為北方政府的進犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座島上的軍方警戒變的更加嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不要到處亂跑比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我只是在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亞美 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你辦件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 二號目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輔助武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風向變了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西南方向 順風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正 三號目標
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對我這麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分數不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過反應值偶爾會極其低下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會集中精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為多愁善感是年輕人的特權
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.03,0:06:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很擔心寺岡古市的情況嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況在新兵中也很常見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心想著出成果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等放下心的時候 心情就會一落千丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別讓我失望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹給你打過電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保準嚇你一跳 超超超大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 快說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…他回來了 回尖端島了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴他姐姐在宿舍以後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說讓我打電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我們家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 到演武廣場去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那裡談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指竹原明之嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴密警戒他自己的住宅 竹原龍藏的診所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及有可能與他接觸的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西村春怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著不管就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實之種因孤獨而心碎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 開始沉悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 旁邊一盆 沒開花的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是休診日吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪費了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那樣…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 請進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候應該說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我回來了」 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之回到島上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在大概去見龍藏醫生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之的朋友來我們家告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然感覺有些不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的名字非常好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐總算到了 娜琪亞美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你認識她嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拯救的那個靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有石化 現在仍然活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候…你說過的吧 會讓他平安的回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早點把他帶回來?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綠先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是姐姐你叫我來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽話 快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想呆在明之的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之對我而言 永遠都是無可替代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 擅自把他帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你母親了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想算是…不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 好歹把房間打掃一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼髒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這已經算是比較整潔的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡 要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是問這回你又在研究什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這座島上也不怎麼太平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那右臂 是校車爆炸時受的傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 類似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是個有才能的「庸醫」 你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著父母的事情只有初戀就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 看起來雖然挺那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希洛克嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你見個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我救了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能用一兩句話就解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她還留有一點思考能力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請裝做沒看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我能原諒這位卉孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想原諒她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我能這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿在你身上的希洛克想去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也只是在尋求答案的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受到了指引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺…大家都想成為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹原明之有可能已經潛伏在裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡待機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦發現對像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即要求各配置點增援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是竹原龍藏醫生吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有一些有關令郎的問題要問…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你也能喜歡我家的橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打擾你休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我的腰就是不爭氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 阿兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來急診了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風紗特製健康雙層便當
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待您再次惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得明之回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最近她不知怎麼回事 一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她一直就只顧看著前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能拜託的人只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這一點還真像春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙真的一直是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 小綠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊裡的事沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已經被開除了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯時回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定時報告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未確認到對像回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其母親也未有異常舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告確認
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒位置變更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置 對象就讀的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水裡有鐵銹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想結束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…回答呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這孩子老是愛惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訓斥他的時候倒是裝出一副再也不犯了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天卻又想出別的什麼鬼點子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後只好把他關在門外禁止吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還對鄰居們說 「只要發現他往家裡鑽 就揍他」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從診所後山潛入廚房的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:18:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當我想「他差不多該求饒了吧」而準備放他進來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在道歉的時候 臉上沾了好多飯粒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到廚房一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小子的晚飯…居然少一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時已經消了氣 非常驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的兒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的兒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 喜歡惡作劇也要有個限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們為這孩子的行蹤 忙得焦頭爛額的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻悄悄的回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我給你打過電話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定過一陣子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹這點 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是他母親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺因為一些事情想見你卻見不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髮型很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼回來了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又想來見我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你的話 我就必須向上面報告你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你來見我的話 我是按耐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我又不想把你交給軍方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能見你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我還是無可救藥的想見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於不知道自己想要什麼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能得到那些東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擁有你所沒有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是12厘米的身高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:20:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼來這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.61,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的東西 這傢伙全都得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.78,0:21:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所擁有的東西都是我渴望得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 我就是那12厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的希洛克和憎恨產生了共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希洛克?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 他是扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內褲都破了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.11,0:21:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得一分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直在努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日以繼夜 孜孜不倦地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事一點意義都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果才是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否被選中才是關鍵 不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 現在心情好像很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於千瘡百孔 成癡成狂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛是妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於相隔千里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.09,0:24:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光與影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的時刻即將到來

